POSITION SUMMARY:
The Principal Application Developer will work in a team of front-end engineers to create responsive, scalable and robust SmartCompliance web applications. We are using the AngularJS framework and calling Java-based API backend RESTful Webservices. We are moving from a traditional tightly coupled three tier architecture using Java Spring MVC framework to a de-coupled Angular based front end MVC architecture with Java API backend services. This is the perfect time for an enthusiastic engineer to add your knowledge of API's, RESTful interfaces, SPA based and responsive design to the team so that we can deliver a superior user experience to ADP SmartCompliance users! 
